 ~/ t.LATRtripsam
 ~/ pm Local Area Trip Generation Rates
 ~/ usage: emme2 clear 321 batch -m "t.LATRtripsam"
 ~/
 ~/ mo01 md01 - trips internal to area
 ~/ mo02 md02 - trips external to area
 ~/ mo03 md03 - total trips
 ~/ mo05 md05 - external station adjustment factor
 ~/ mo06 md06 - sq.ft. of general office less than 25000 square feet
 ~/ mo07 md07 - sq.ft. of general office greater than 25000 square feet
 ~/ mo08 md08 - number of general offices greater than 25000 square feet 
 ~/ mo09 md09 - sq.ft. of single employer greater than 300000 square feet
 ~/ mo10 md10 - number of single employer greater than 300000 square feet 
 ~/ mo11 md11 - GLA of retail center under 50000 with food store
 ~/ mo12 md12 - number of retail centers under 50000 with food store
 ~/ mo13 md13 - GLA of retail center over 50000 with food store
 ~/ mo14 md14 - number of retail centers over 50000 with food store
 ~/ mo15 md15 - GLA of retail center under 50000 without food store
 ~/ mo16 md16 - number of retail centers under 50000 without food store
 ~/ mo17 md17 - GLA of retail center over 50000 without food store
 ~/ mo18 md18 - number of retail centers over 50000 without food store
 ~/ mo19 md19 - number of single family detached units
 ~/ mo20 md20 - number of townhouses (single family attached)
 ~/ mo21 md21 - number of garden apartment units
 ~/ mo22 md22 - number of high-rise apartment units
 ~/ mo30 md30 - distance of centroid to Rail Station
 ~/
 ~/ ##############################
 ~/ TRANSPOSE LANDUSE
 ~/ ##############################
 ~/
